fulltitle: EP 3.11: Dave Holland talks responsibility, publishing rights, and social media [#fhtz]
description:
“After the gig I usually go out and talk to people, have a little time to interact. I see social media as an extension of that, humanising what we do.”  - Dave Holland

We close Season 3 with the legendary jazz bassist, record producer and record company owner Dave Holland. Dave has been in the music business for over half a century, has played with other legends such as Miles Davis and Chick Corea, and won different awards. It was an honour talking with him and learning about his views on the responsibilities that musicians have, opportunities and threats of digital, live recordings for web-exclusive releases and more. A must-watch interview filled with great insights from a living legend.

Produced by Simon Kurt & Sebastiano Mereu for Digitale Massarbeit & Digital Fanfare
